These are Puzzles for 1x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-1::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: purple, red, mauve, lavender, orange, amber
1. the person who likes red is the person who likes red##1
2. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
3. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the person who likes orange##5
4. the person who likes purple is not to the left of the person who likes amber##8
5. the person who likes mauve is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
7. the person who likes lavender is between the person who likes purple and the person who likes amber##2
8. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |      4       |   5    |   6   |
| Color   | orange | red | amber | lavender | purple | mauve |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-2::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  freelancer, social-worker, doctor, paramedic, electrician, teacher
1. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the doctor##5
2. the paramedic is somewhere to the left of the social-worker##5
3. the freelancer is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
4. the teacher is on the far right##1
5. the freelancer is somewhere to the left of the paramedic##5
6. the paramedic is not to the right of the electrician##8
7. the doctor is on the left or right of the electrician##3
8. the teacher is on the right of the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |  3   |    4     |   5    |   6   |
| Job   | freelancer | paramedic | social-worker | doctor | electrician | teacher |

