.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-4::.
House: modern, futuristic, cottage, gothic-revival, craftsman, cape-cod
1. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the futuristic house##5
2. the cape-cod house is not to the left of the cottage house##8
3. the cape-cod house is not to the right of the modern house##8
4. the craftsman house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
5. the futuristic house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
6. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3

.:: Answer ::.
