.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-5::.
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, colombian, russian, american, pakistani, british
 1. the american is in an odd position##4
 2. the american is not to the left of the russian##8
 3. the british is in an odd position##4
 4. the british is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5
 5. the pakistani is somewhere to the right of the russian##5
 6. the colombian is between the russian and the american##2
 7. the colombian is somewhere between the russian and the american##7
 8. the russian is somewhere to the right of the argentine##5
 9. the american is not to the right of the american##8
10. the pakistani is on the left or right of the american##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |    4     |   5   |       6       |
| Nationality   | british | argentine | russian | colombian | american | pakistani |

