.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-6::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: trance, ambient, techno, classical, blues, funk
1. the fan of trance is somewhere between the fan of techno and the fan of ambient##7
2. the fan of funk is not to the right of the fan of ambient##8
3. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
4. the fan of classical is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of blues##1
6. the fan of funk is somewhere to the left of the fan of classical##5
7. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the fan of techno##5
8. the fan of classical is somewhere between the fan of techno and the fan of trance##7

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |   2    |   3    |     4      |    5     |  6  |
| Music-Genre   | funk | techno | classical | trance | ambient | blues |

