.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-7::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: april, december, october, february, august, march
1. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
4. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##8
5. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##8
6. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in april##2
7. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8
8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
9. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |    5     |       6       |
| Birthday   | february | october | august | april | december | march |

